                        <div class="textBox mb-30">
                            The University of Science and Technology of Yemen aspires to become one of the most
                            prestigious
                            universities at the regional and global levels, and works to achieve this goal by raising
                            the
                            level of performance in all aspects, especially academic ones, by providing the appropriate
                            environments to provide distinguished education and effective learning, implement advanced
                            studies and research projects, and provide distinguished services to the community.
                            <br/>
                            <br/>
                            The campus includes everything a student needs for learning, training or activity, from
                            classrooms with international educational specifications, a central library that serves all
                            specializations, and a central library that serves the university's specializations, in
                            addition
                            to the graduate studies hall and the grand hall for training university students, a seminar
                            hall
                            for scientific activities and seminars. Engineering and electronics laboratories and
                            computer
                            labs. The university also provided sports equipment and a gym. Audio-visual halls. Research
                            and
                            development centers. A seminar hall, training halls and a workshop hall. Modern and advanced
                            laboratories, spacious green spaces, a distinguished student lounge and many other features.
                        </div>
